data.description: Welcome to Art Foundry located in Atlantic Station in the heart of Midtown Atlanta. Listed is a 1st floor 1 bed/1 bath unit with an open floor plan. It has hardwood flooring throughout, 10ft ceilings, and a screened in porch. The kitchen is lined with granite counter tops, upper and lower cabinet storage space, stainless steel appliances, and space for sitting at the counter. In the bathroom there is a dual vanity with granite counters, tile in the standup shower as well as a bathtub/shower combination and a walk-in closet. The master bedroom is spacious with natural light. Art Foundry is a neighbor friendly community that offers great amenities like: a well-equipped gym, spa and sauna rooms, 24-hour security, pets, an EV charging station, and a well gated parking garage. The best part of living here is the LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION!!! You would be a 10-minute walk from Atlantic Station where there are a plethora of restaurants and shops, a 5 minute drive to I-75/I-85 as well as Westside Provisions and the newly built Interlock that has everything from family fun Putt Putt to a Holiday bar for a cute date night. If you want city living, Art Foundry is the place!
